    <li class="comment-item" data-cid="1173894089">
        <div class="comment">
            <h3>
                <span class="comment-vote">
                    <span id="c-1173894089" class="vote-count">0</span>
                        <a href="javascript:;" id="btn-1173894089" class="j a_show_login" data-cid="1173894089">有用</a>
                </span>
                <span class="comment-info">
                    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/DebraRomer/">衛藤美彩</a>
                        <span class="user-stars allstar50 rating" title="力荐"></span>
                    <span>2017-04-05</span>
                </span>
            </h3>
            <p class="comment-content">仅《孔子与春秋》。钱氏雕工学案，之前看的三本均非钱最强领域。语言很平和，通俗路线，没走《师友杂忆》文言路子。风格有模仿顾颉刚的意味，引用典籍逊于顾老，学问阅读量非同一等级。可他终是大家，用汉以春秋非论语、官学孔子，尽见眼界高远。第五章至第七章，钱穆突然发力，功力尽显。</p>
        </div>
    </li>

                
    <li class="comment-item" data-cid="1116097556">
